text: "Live Those Songs" is a song by Kenny Chesney. ==Music video== The music video was directed by Shaun Silva and was premiered on CMT on February 26, 2004. The video debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of April 8, 2004. The music video reached number 1 on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for the week of June 17, 2004. ==References== Category:2002 songs Category:Kenny Chesney songs Category:Music videos directed by Shaun Silva
